Package it.polimi.ingsw.server.view

Interface Interviewer

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    RMIView, SocketView, View
    public interface Interviewer
    Core of the IO of the client-server message-based architecture. This interface is an high-level API use by the server to communicate to the client, communicating questions and receiving answers
